OL,3,CDad of Southport attacker warned
OL,4,Cteacher he may become violent
OL,6,FThe father of the Southport attacker
OL,7,Fwarned a teacher who attempted to
OL,8,Fvisit him at home that the teenager
OL,9,Fmay become violent if forced to see
OL,10,Fhim, a public inquiry has heard.
OL,12,FLucy McLoughlin, headteacher of
OL,13,Fspecialist autistic school Presfield
OL,14,FHigh, told the Southport Inquiry AR -
OL,15,Fas he is know - was transferred to the
OL,16,Fschool from a pupil referral unit in
OL,17,FMarch 2022 but school from a pupil
OL,18,Freferral unit in March 2022 but had an
OL,19,Fattendance record of 0.7%.
