OL,3,CDad of Southport attacker warned
OL,4,Cteacher he may become violent
OL,6,FHe was removed from the school's roll
OL,7,Fin June 2024 and the following month,
OL,8,Fon 29 July, the then 17-year-old
OL,9,Fmurdered Elsie Dot Stancombe, seven,
OL,10,FBebe King, six, and Alice da Silva
OL,11,FAguiar, nine, in a knife attack on a
OL,12,FTaylor Swift-themed dance class.
OL,14,FMs McLoughlin told the inquiry,
OL,15,Fsitting at Liverpool Town Hall, that
OL,16,Fduring his time at the school a number
OL,17,Fof members of staff visited his home
OL,18,Fbut were not allowed to see him.
