OL,3,CDad of Southport attacker warned
OL,4,Cteacher he may become violent
OL,6,FShe confirmed in May 2022 his form
OL,7,Ftutor, James Berry, carried out a home
OL,8,Fvisit and was given a "warning" by his
OL,9,Ffather, Alphonse.
OL,11,FDavid Temkin KC, representing families
OL,12,Fof children who survived the attack,
OL,13,Fasked Ms McLoughlin: "Was that warning
OL,14,Fthat AR may become violent and may
OL,15,Fattack Mr Berry if AR was forced to
OL,16,Fsee him?"
OL,18,FShe replied: "Yes."
