OL,3,CDad of Southport attacker warned
OL,4,Cteacher he may become violent
OL,6,FShe said the warning was reported to
OL,7,Fthe school's safeguarding lead and
OL,8,Ffollowing that staff were accompanied
OL,9,Fby a Merseyside Police safer schools
OL,10,Fofficer when they attended.
OL,12,FMs McLoughlin said she had carried out
OL,13,Fa number of visits to the home, in
OL,14,FBanks, Lancashire, but had been told
OL,15,Fshe could not see the teenager by his
OL,16,Fmother, Laetitia Muzayire.
OL,18,F"AR's mother would say 'not today' and
OL,19,Fpush us away from that," she said.
