OL,6,F"Sometimes there was no answer at the
OL,7,Fdoor.
OL,9,F"One time I managed to get in to the
OL,10,Flounge and AR refused to come down and
OL,11,Frefused to be seen. There was no way
OL,12,Fto see him."
OL,14,FAsked if a reason was given for the
OL,15,Frefusals, Ms McLoughlin said
OL,16,F"Sometimes he was sleeping, sometimes
OL,17,Fhe just did not want to see us."
OL,19,FShe said the school tried different
OL,20,Fways to engage AR when he first joined.
