OL,3,CDad of Southport attacker warned
OL,4,Cteacher he may become violent
OL,6,FShe said: "He came in and played
OL,7,Fbasketball with his form tutor to get
OL,8,Fa feel of the building, to build those
OL,9,Fpositive relationships.
OL,11,F"He'd come in when it was his
OL,12,Ffavourite lunch, so he'd come in and
OL,13,Fhave pizza.
OL,15,F"When AR's father said the classroom
OL,16,Fwas too busy, we then took him out of
OL,17,Fthe classroom and he was taught one to
OL,18,Fone."
