OL,6,FShe said he also had specialist input
OL,7,Ffrom a speech and language therapist
OL,8,Fand an occupational therapist, who
OL,9,Fplayed chess with him to try and build
OL,10,Fa relationship.
OL,12,FThe inquiry has heard AR was
OL,13,Fpermanently excluded from Range High
OL,14,FSchool in Formby in 2019 after he
OL,15,Fadmitted carrying knives.
OL,17,FHe later returned to the school, again
OL,18,Fcarrying a knife, and assaulted
OL,19,Fanother pupil with a hockey stick.
