OL,4,Cteacher he may become violent
OL,6,FMs McLoughlin said full details of his
OL,7,Fhistory, in particular his intent to
OL,8,Fstab someone, were not included in his
OL,9,Feducation, health and care plan
OL,10,F(EHCP), and if they had been the
OL,11,Fschool would not have accepted him.
OL,13,FShe said: "Children there are
OL,14,Fextremely vulnerable, if we had that
OL,15,Finformation we would not have been
OL,16,Fable to meet AR's needs."
OL,18,FThe inquiry continues.
